s as a\nfunction of $n$. We obtain, for example, that maximal independent set, on\ntrees, requires $\\Omega(\\log n / \\log \\log n)$ rounds for deterministic\nalgorithms, which is tight.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 20:41:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 19:50:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 10:12:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
