s are validated and evaluated by extensive simulation\nstudies or real data applications. Relevant comparative studies demonstrate the\nsuperiority of the developed outlier detection method with other competitors in\ndistributional outlier detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Oct 2021 01:52:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
